Contact Form
Have a specific question or inquiry? Fill out the form below, and I’ll get back to you as soon as possible.


&lt;label for="name" class="form-label"&gt;Name&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Your Name"&gt;


&lt;label for="email" class="form-label"&gt;Email&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="your.email@example.com"&gt;


&lt;label for="subject" class="form-label"&gt;Subject&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="subject" placeholder="What is this regarding?"&gt;


&lt;label for="message" class="form-label"&gt;Message&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="5" placeholder="Your message here..."&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;


Send Message

Location
Currently based in Boston, Massachusetts, I’m open to remote opportunities as well as positions in the Greater Boston area.


&lt;h3 class="card-title"&gt;Boston, MA&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class="card-text"&gt;
  Boston is a hub for education, technology, and innovation, home to numerous universities and tech companies. It's an exciting place to be for someone in the fields of data analytics and technology.
&lt;/p&gt;
